{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"战地重逢","authors":["李松涛"],"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":6,"day":27}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战地重逢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李松涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重返战地访校园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声惊呼急握手——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个当年的红卫兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧遇恰在校门口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逢战友，思绪稠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮涌似大江流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暂不问——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你下乡远征进戈壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎为沙海披锦绣？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日又回母校来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再接进军突击手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暂不说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他到边陲守国门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎胜北疆风雪骤？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天又到老家来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再接兵营新战友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且看旧貌变新颜哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜景处处瞧不够："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看操场——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗似火迎风抖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看大路——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学工学农涌人流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屏息听，凝神瞅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环顾校园伫立久。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！不斗争就不能进步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争历程记心头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……往事桩桩难忘怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十七年，修正主义迷雾罩高楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席一声动员令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命风雷吼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇恨迸出膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒火驱笔走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你呀——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哗”的抖开大字报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啪”的贴到校门口——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"质问走资派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗炮弹惊高楼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为什么培养“小宝塔”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为什么专讲“学而优”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为什么不批“三家村”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为什么大搞封、资、修？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声问，声声吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大字报前摆战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命师生亮矛头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，革命洪流滚滚来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激浪排空驾飞舟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资派，无处溜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗中策划新阴谋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月晴空天突变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴云汹涌遮日头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资派，变花样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“消防”的“水枪”喷突突。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"校门口撕下大字报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声称运动要有“步骤”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沸腾的学校哑下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霎时山呆水不流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资派——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对革命师生搞镇压，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一顶“反党”的大帽子呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无情地往你头上扣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鹰不怕悬崖陡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战舸敢向浪里游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴风呼啸山不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑手难挡大江流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是他呀——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑云压城城欲摧时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着走资派坚持斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资派要护“旧”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走的不是一股道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转的不是一条轴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个阶级在较量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两条路线在搏斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他把一张大字报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴到校门口——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“走资派对群众运动不支持，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是扼杀革命的刽子手！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“镇压革命罪滔天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色恐怖不长久！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捅了马蜂窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扒了老虎口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是他也成了“反党分子”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块作了牢中“囚”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小巴掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能捂住火山口？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"区区螳臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能拦住列车走？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，毛主席挥手扫阴云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日万里照神州。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破牢门见阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧起“十六条”热泪流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友携手又上阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥棒痛打落水狗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"校门口又写大字报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺天盖地来势骤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直指叛徒、内奸、工贼刘少奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擒贼须先擒贼首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘胜追击惊雷奔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排山倒海写春秋……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了哇忘不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万山红遍凯歌奏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你俩——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又用大字报写申请，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴在革委会牌前校门口："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《要到边疆做苍松》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《要到戈壁做红柳》。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志在雪山斗寒冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志在沙海建绿洲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旗招展万旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵结队雄赳赳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱知道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——战斗正未有穷期，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级斗争不停休。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年百载难到头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要提高警惕长期斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风头上认输的走资派呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在一旁冷眼瞅……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年岁月斗争中过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友重逢在校门口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天南地北豪情壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经风历雨向前走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！握握当年攥战笔的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——如今老茧铜钱厚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！拍拍当年扛战旗的肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——如今更是有劲头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，看这校门口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么满眼稠？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬！又是一茬大字报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮声隆隆在战斗："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“反击右倾翻案风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育革命方向不容扭！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“掌握批邓大方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命更上一层楼。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字句句象排炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开批判党内资产阶级的战斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好哇！好哇！校门口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年烽烟战未休。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资派还在走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级在战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是声讨！是批判！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大会场，人声吼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士又闻战鼓响呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗志勃发满心头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里有炮声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里去战斗："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“走！咱俩也去参战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争中会合新战友！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命锻炼的新一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！革命路上永远不停留。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"教育革命","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}